TITLE

   MFR - MagicFileRequester

VERSION

   2.0 - Major update to 1.3b

AUTHOR

   Stefan Stuntz (stuntz@informatik.tu-muenchen.de)

DESCRIPTION

   MFR is a replacement for all other file requesters.
   Features include complete keyboard control, nice outfit,
   proportional font support, directory caching, file find
   mechanism, file class support, file notification, many
   configuration options, history list, ...

NEW FEATURES

   Major changes from 1.3b are

   - Improved directory caching (up to 100 directories).
   - New gadget & list handling, should be much more comfortablen now.
   - Filename completion.
   - New memory management.
   - History list.
   - Function key support.
   - Improved compatibility with asl and reqtools.
   - Faster directory reading.
   - Many small bug fixes and enhancements.

   For detailed information, refer to the History file of the
   distribution archive. It's very long this time.

